1
00:00:15,773 --> 00:00:21,948
[Gao Zhun]

2
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:28,800
Mr. Gao.

3
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,520
It's late.

4
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:33,200
What's the matter?

5
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:36,619
<i>The letter.</i>

6
00:00:36,619 --> 00:00:38,600
<i>I received it.</i>

7
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,960
I'm sorry.

8
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:44,920
I shouldn't have sulked.

9
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,320
Why did you sulk?

10
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,000
<i>I just...</i>

11
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:56,680
I couldn't stand that you gave
that boy your business card.

12
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:59,960
I can't stand it when you're as good
to others as you are to me.

13
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:04,040
I just want you to be good to me.

14
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:06,040
<i>I just want you to look at me.</i>

15
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,640
I...

16
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:10,480
I get jealous.

17
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,880
Cut!

18
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:15,100
Good. That's a wrap.

19
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,680
Thank you, Director.

20
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,920
Gentlemen.

21
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:24,000
We're shooting the promotional posters
tomorrow morning.

22
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,360
Please get some rest tonight.

23
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,640
The makeup and departure times...

24
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:29,360
I'll sync them with your assistants later.

25
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,360
Thank you.

26
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,040
Good work.

27
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:36,520
Gao Zhun was difficult because of jealousy.

28
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,440
But what about you?

29
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,920
Do you need me to write you a letter?

30
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,440
There's no need.

31
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,800
The show is just fiction.

32
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:55,173
The car is here. Let's go.

33
00:01:55,173 --> 00:01:56,600
Okay.

34
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,280
See you tomorrow, Mr. Zhen.

35
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,800
See you tomorrow.

36
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,780
The car is here for us, too.

37
00:03:35,393 --> 00:03:39,429
[Episode 7]

38
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,760
Soften the top light a bit more.

39
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,280
Let's see it from the side.

40
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,760
Yesterday's scene...

41
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,480
I still haven't quite recovered from it.

42
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,760
The hardest part is over.

43
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,320
It'll be easier from here on.

44
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,320
Hey.

45
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:08,000
How are things going for you two?

46
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,440
Quite smoothly.

47
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,720
Wu.

48
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,760
Zhun.

49
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,760
Wu, your sugar-free latte.

50
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,760
Zhun.

51
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,240
Not bad. You still remember my preference.

52
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,947
Of course.

53
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,727
Zhun.

54
00:04:21,727 --> 00:04:23,440
I saw today's shooting schedule.

55
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,560
Today, there's...

56
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,560
a kiss scene.

57
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:31,320
Wu Rong, you have some heavy dark circles.

58
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,800
Didn't get enough rest?

59
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,320
Don't even ask.

60
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:36,400
I had a fight with my wife over the phone.

61
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,760
She really pissed me off.

62
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:40,120
But it's fine now.

63
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,720
As long as you're okay.

64
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,800
- Wu Rong.
- Yeah?

65
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:52,360
Since you're filming this,
doesn't your wife mind?

66
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,960
She's my wife.

67
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,720
It's different from a girlfriend.

68
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:58,480
You can break up with a girlfriend at any time.

69
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:01,400
But would a wife divorce you over a role?

70
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,680
What do you mean a girlfriend
can break up at any time?

71
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,480
Zhun and his fiancée won't.

72
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:12,040
They have a great relationship.

73
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,800
Right.

74
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,760
Hey, Zhun.

75
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,240
Who was that just now?

76
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,800
Hey.

77
00:05:29,722 --> 00:05:31,522
That psycho...

78
00:05:31,522 --> 00:05:33,442
He didn't mess with you yesterday, did he?

79
00:05:33,442 --> 00:05:34,962
Wu, Zhun.

80
00:05:34,962 --> 00:05:37,522
Which psycho are you talking about?

81
00:05:37,522 --> 00:05:39,722
Don't butt in on adult business, kid. Go.

82
00:05:39,722 --> 00:05:41,722
All right, then. I'll get back to work.

83
00:05:43,722 --> 00:05:44,882
Your state is very good.

84
00:05:44,882 --> 00:05:46,482
Keep it up.

85
00:05:47,442 --> 00:05:49,042
Okay.

86
00:05:51,082 --> 00:05:52,882
Perfect.

87
00:05:52,882 --> 00:05:54,482
Look here.

88
00:05:56,922 --> 00:05:59,002
Good. Let's change the pose.

89
00:06:00,402 --> 00:06:02,882
- Okay.
- Why are there so many flowers?

90
00:06:02,882 --> 00:06:04,840
The poster uses the language of flowers
as a metaphor for the characters.

91
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,840
- Look here.
- So, we prepared several kinds.

92
00:06:07,802 --> 00:06:09,642
Okay.

93
00:06:09,642 --> 00:06:11,442
So professional.

94
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,562
As expected of you, Mr. Zhen.

95
00:06:13,562 --> 00:06:15,802
The success rate of these shots is amazing.

96
00:06:15,802 --> 00:06:17,242
Red roses are passionate...

97
00:06:17,242 --> 00:06:18,242
and seductive.

98
00:06:18,242 --> 00:06:19,722
They suit you.

99
00:06:19,722 --> 00:06:21,040
Gao Zhun...

100
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,482
Red roses don't suit him.

101
00:06:22,482 --> 00:06:24,442
Of course they don't.

102
00:06:25,762 --> 00:06:30,322
Gao Zhun's love... is clean and pure.

103
00:06:30,322 --> 00:06:33,722
In his world, there is no calculation.

104
00:06:38,442 --> 00:06:42,802
Only white roses can express his pure heart.

105
00:06:48,782 --> 00:06:50,402
The character arc between us

106
00:06:50,402 --> 00:06:52,202
should naturally follow my perspective.

107
00:06:52,202 --> 00:06:55,320
Mr. Zhen, aren't you overstepping a bit?

108
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,362
The scene centers on Gao Zhun.

109
00:06:57,362 --> 00:06:59,040
He is the core.

110
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:03,282
Or are you habitually

111
00:07:03,282 --> 00:07:05,042
trying to upstage him?

112
00:07:09,802 --> 00:07:12,122
You're the photographer, you call the shots.

113
00:07:12,122 --> 00:07:14,002
Me?

114
00:07:15,162 --> 00:07:16,842
Then let's try everything.

115
00:07:16,842 --> 00:07:18,282
Which pair is going first?

116
00:07:18,282 --> 00:07:19,282
Me.

117
00:07:19,282 --> 00:07:21,442
Lest I have to follow his lead.

118
00:07:23,602 --> 00:07:26,162
Why are you laughing? I'm not wrong.

119
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,802
Guys, can you be more affectionate?

120
00:07:43,802 --> 00:07:45,482
I'm already holding him, aren't I?

121
00:07:45,482 --> 00:07:48,042
It's not sensual enough.

122
00:07:48,042 --> 00:07:49,882
How about this? Mr. Wu, take off some clothes.

123
00:07:49,882 --> 00:07:52,000
Do some push-ups before we start.

124
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,560
Fine.

125
00:08:05,842 --> 00:08:07,442
Let's do this.

126
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,802
Come on.

127
00:08:12,802 --> 00:08:15,362
Yes! That's the "forced love" vibe I want.

128
00:08:15,362 --> 00:08:16,842
Nice.

129
00:08:18,242 --> 00:08:19,922
Press down a bit more.

130
00:08:19,922 --> 00:08:21,962
A little more.

131
00:08:22,882 --> 00:08:25,522
Okay, Mr. Wu is done.

132
00:08:25,522 --> 00:08:27,522
Next pair, get ready.

133
00:08:46,442 --> 00:08:47,942
Come on.

134
00:08:49,402 --> 00:08:51,082
What?

135
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:54,360
To destroy your rose?

136
00:08:55,202 --> 00:08:56,742
I can't bring myself to do it.

137
00:08:56,742 --> 00:08:59,920
Zhen Xin. We're shooting a poster.

138
00:09:01,011 --> 00:09:02,813
I know.

139
00:09:02,813 --> 00:09:04,835
But I just can't bear to.

140
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,360
Okay.

141
00:09:21,002 --> 00:09:23,362
Let's do another set, but tone it down.

142
00:09:23,362 --> 00:09:25,322
Or the promo materials won't get approved.

143
00:09:29,042 --> 00:09:31,682
I wanted to tell you that day...

144
00:09:31,682 --> 00:09:33,762
The acting is fake,

145
00:09:33,762 --> 00:09:35,682
but I am serious.

146
00:09:51,602 --> 00:09:52,922
Good.

147
00:09:52,922 --> 00:09:54,642
Great, amazing!

148
00:09:54,642 --> 00:09:56,082
Hold that.

149
00:09:56,082 --> 00:09:58,640
Yes, that's it. Again.

150
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:00,360
Okay.

151
00:10:07,922 --> 00:10:09,522
I have something to discuss with Mr. Zhen.

152
00:10:09,522 --> 00:10:11,482
Could you watch the door for me?

153
00:10:14,602 --> 00:10:16,242
Okay.

154
00:10:20,762 --> 00:10:22,322
Mr. Wu.

155
00:10:22,322 --> 00:10:24,402
What's your advice?

156
00:10:24,402 --> 00:10:27,160
Did you not take a single word I said to heart?

157
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:29,962
- I did.
- Then why are you still pestering him?

158
00:10:31,082 --> 00:10:33,402
Yes. You're a Best Actor winner.

159
00:10:33,402 --> 00:10:35,722
You're young, reckless, and at your peak.

160
00:10:35,722 --> 00:10:37,042
You can afford to make mistakes.

161
00:10:37,042 --> 00:10:39,682
Starry Entertainment will always
protect you as their top star.

162
00:10:39,682 --> 00:10:41,002
But what about Zhun?

163
00:10:41,002 --> 00:10:42,762
He doesn't have as many chances as you.

164
00:10:42,762 --> 00:10:44,162
He can't afford to lose,

165
00:10:44,162 --> 00:10:45,880
and he can't afford to make a mistake.

166
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:48,282
This is between Zhang Zhun and me.

167
00:10:48,282 --> 00:10:50,002
Even if you're his senior,

168
00:10:50,002 --> 00:10:53,122
you shouldn't interfere in our relationship.

169
00:10:53,122 --> 00:10:54,762
How dare you even mention a relationship!

170
00:10:54,762 --> 00:10:56,162
What are your intentions for Zhun?

171
00:10:56,162 --> 00:10:58,082
Do you think I'm blind?

172
00:11:00,002 --> 00:11:02,602
I'm sorry, Mr. Zhang.
It's not convenient for you to go in now.

173
00:11:02,602 --> 00:11:03,722
Yes.

174
00:11:03,722 --> 00:11:06,322
I just want to get into Zhang Zhun's bed.

175
00:11:06,322 --> 00:11:08,002
- Holy shit!
- Hush.

176
00:11:08,002 --> 00:11:10,042
It's a misunderstanding, all of it.

177
00:11:10,042 --> 00:11:11,482
I like him.

178
00:11:11,482 --> 00:11:14,322
On and off screen, I like him.

179
00:11:14,322 --> 00:11:16,202
- Why you little...
- Don't come in!

180
00:11:16,202 --> 00:11:17,522
Zhun.

181
00:11:17,522 --> 00:11:19,042
Wu Rong.

182
00:11:20,602 --> 00:11:21,882
Zhun.

183
00:11:21,882 --> 00:11:23,282
Wu Rong.

184
00:11:23,282 --> 00:11:25,722
Let us handle our own matters.

185
00:11:26,522 --> 00:11:29,322
Please take Xiao Deng back first.

186
00:11:31,522 --> 00:11:33,162
Wu Rong.

187
00:11:33,842 --> 00:11:35,342
Fuck.

188
00:11:41,962 --> 00:11:44,322
Some jokes should never be made.

189
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:50,362
I'm not joking.

190
00:11:50,362 --> 00:11:51,842
Zhen Xin...

191
00:11:51,842 --> 00:11:53,122
You're not Fang Chi. Wake up.

192
00:11:53,122 --> 00:11:54,562
I am awake. I...

193
00:11:54,562 --> 00:11:57,202
You have no idea what you're doing.

194
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,520
Don't you like me?

195
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:10,682
What's there to like?

196
00:12:10,682 --> 00:12:12,722
We're both straight.

197
00:12:12,722 --> 00:12:14,242
It's impossible.

198
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,160
Why do you avoid me,

199
00:12:38,241 --> 00:12:40,321
but not my kisses?

200
00:12:42,682 --> 00:12:44,682
I...

201
00:12:44,682 --> 00:12:46,602
I haven't thought it through.

202
00:12:46,602 --> 00:12:48,882
Then I'll wait until you have.

203
00:12:50,082 --> 00:12:52,122
No matter what happens,

204
00:12:53,442 --> 00:12:55,882
I'll always be by your side.

205
00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:11,202
This four-panel comic is quite funny.

206
00:13:11,202 --> 00:13:13,962
Mr. Zhang, look.

207
00:13:34,042 --> 00:13:35,682
Look.

208
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:38,922
Isn't it funny?

209
00:13:38,922 --> 00:13:40,762
Yes.

210
00:13:40,762 --> 00:13:42,682
It's quite funny.

211
00:13:50,882 --> 00:13:52,442
You know what to do.

212
00:14:04,482 --> 00:14:05,722
Don't do this.

213
00:14:05,722 --> 00:14:07,442
Someone will see us.

214
00:14:09,802 --> 00:14:12,242
But I just want to hold your hand.

215
00:14:12,242 --> 00:14:14,322
Not just that.

216
00:14:14,322 --> 00:14:17,082
I want to kiss you passionately,

217
00:14:17,842 --> 00:14:20,722
and pull you into my very being.

218
00:14:23,082 --> 00:14:24,082
Let's go.

219
00:14:24,082 --> 00:14:25,682
To my place.

220
00:14:38,482 --> 00:14:40,122
Honey!

221
00:14:40,762 --> 00:14:43,842
Honey, why didn't you answer my calls?

222
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:48,120
You must be Mr. Zhang Zhun.

223
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:51,242
Hello, Zhen Xin must have
caused you a lot of trouble.

224
00:14:51,242 --> 00:14:52,742
No, not at all.

225
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:55,962
Well...

226
00:14:55,962 --> 00:14:58,602
I'll head back to my room now.

227
00:15:00,082 --> 00:15:01,880
Honey.

228
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:03,442
Let's go back to our room, too.

229
00:15:03,442 --> 00:15:05,682
Didn't you miss me?

230
00:15:46,602 --> 00:15:47,722
Honey.

231
00:15:47,722 --> 00:15:50,882
Strawberry or glow-in-the-dark? Pick one.

232
00:15:59,242 --> 00:16:01,362
Honey.

233
00:16:02,482 --> 00:16:04,122
You saw all that just now, right?

234
00:16:04,122 --> 00:16:06,122
Saw what?

235
00:16:06,122 --> 00:16:07,722
You tell me.

236
00:16:07,722 --> 00:16:09,122
Oh!

237
00:16:09,122 --> 00:16:10,482
I ship it! I totally ship it!

238
00:16:10,482 --> 00:16:11,602
Happy now?

239
00:16:11,602 --> 00:16:14,602
That was for work. I understand.

240
00:16:14,602 --> 00:16:18,162
You know I'm not a petty woman.

241
00:16:20,002 --> 00:16:22,482
I've had the crew get you a room.

242
00:16:23,442 --> 00:16:25,840
You'll stay there for the next few days.

243
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,680
Get some rest.

244
00:16:28,442 --> 00:16:30,962
I'm going out for a walk.

245
00:16:30,962 --> 00:16:33,762
Honey, what do you mean by this?

246
00:17:01,802 --> 00:17:05,082
Give me more time. I'll sort it out.

247
00:17:17,882 --> 00:17:19,762
When did you two start dating?

248
00:17:19,762 --> 00:17:23,680
We got together this time last year.

249
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,473
It's been almost a year.

250
00:17:25,473 --> 00:17:26,642
Honey.

251
00:17:26,642 --> 00:17:30,802
They're so annoying, asking questions.

252
00:17:30,802 --> 00:17:33,522
Are you being so open about things
because you want to go public?

253
00:17:33,522 --> 00:17:35,122
Is that not allowed?

254
00:17:47,442 --> 00:17:48,922
He's so handsome.

255
00:17:48,922 --> 00:17:51,242
I couldn't tell yesterday.

256
00:17:52,362 --> 00:17:54,802
He looks better in person.

257
00:17:54,802 --> 00:17:56,442
He looks very natural.

258
00:17:56,442 --> 00:17:57,962
Today's makeup and styling...

259
00:17:57,962 --> 00:17:59,042
is too pretentious.

260
00:17:59,042 --> 00:18:00,122
Oh.

261
00:18:00,122 --> 00:18:02,242
So, you don't like him in character.

262
00:18:02,242 --> 00:18:04,602
You like him as himself.

263
00:18:08,282 --> 00:18:09,522
Zhang Zhun.

264
00:18:09,522 --> 00:18:11,102
Why are your eyes so swollen?

265
00:18:11,102 --> 00:18:12,362
They're bloodshot, too.

266
00:18:12,362 --> 00:18:14,480
Didn't you sleep well last night?

267
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,682
Last night...

268
00:18:15,682 --> 00:18:17,042
There were mosquitoes in the room.

269
00:18:17,042 --> 00:18:19,520
They kept me awake with their biting.

270
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,362
Mr. Zhang, try this.

271
00:18:21,362 --> 00:18:22,362
It'll clear up the redness.

272
00:18:22,362 --> 00:18:24,202
Don't let it affect the shoot.

273
00:18:24,202 --> 00:18:25,402
Mr. Zhang.

274
00:18:25,402 --> 00:18:26,902
Let me do it.

275
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,402
Don't worry.

276
00:18:29,402 --> 00:18:31,722
I'm an expert at applying eye drops.

277
00:18:34,162 --> 00:18:35,522
Then I'll trouble you.

278
00:18:35,522 --> 00:18:37,962
Here. Come on.

279
00:18:47,362 --> 00:18:50,242
It's heartbreaking to see you in tears.

280
00:18:50,242 --> 00:18:52,362
You must be a natural at crying scenes.

281
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,722
All departments, get ready.

282
00:19:04,722 --> 00:19:06,202
Three, two, one.

283
00:19:06,202 --> 00:19:07,802
Action.

284
00:19:09,882 --> 00:19:12,122
What will you think about after you go back?

285
00:19:14,322 --> 00:19:16,082
About you.

286
00:19:28,522 --> 00:19:30,802
Is this distance acceptable?

287
00:19:31,762 --> 00:19:33,262
Yes.

288
00:19:34,882 --> 00:19:36,562
How about this?

289
00:19:37,962 --> 00:19:40,002
Like this?

290
00:19:40,002 --> 00:19:42,362
It's a bit strange.

291
00:19:42,362 --> 00:19:45,922
Now, let's try touching.

292
00:19:58,962 --> 00:20:00,962
Can you stop?

293
00:20:02,322 --> 00:20:05,082
You can try to endure it a bit longer.

294
00:20:05,802 --> 00:20:07,922
Cut!

295
00:20:07,922 --> 00:20:10,202
No, no, no. That's all wrong.

296
00:20:10,202 --> 00:20:11,722
What's wrong, Director?

297
00:20:11,722 --> 00:20:14,402
Zhen Xin, at this point in the story,

298
00:20:14,402 --> 00:20:15,402
your feelings for Zhang Zhun...

299
00:20:15,402 --> 00:20:17,522
haven't reached that level yet, got it?

300
00:20:17,522 --> 00:20:19,402
- Zhang Zhun...
- Oh, my mistake.

301
00:20:19,402 --> 00:20:21,642
Gao Zhun, Gao Zhun.

302
00:20:21,642 --> 00:20:23,962
I just felt this would have more tension.

303
00:20:23,962 --> 00:20:25,842
If we follow your logic,

304
00:20:25,842 --> 00:20:27,802
we'd have to clear the set
for every dialogue scene.

305
00:20:27,802 --> 00:20:30,122
No. This isn't the vibe I want at all.

306
00:20:30,122 --> 00:20:32,042
Adjust it, quickly.

307
00:20:34,962 --> 00:20:38,402
Honey, have some water and take a break.

308
00:20:38,402 --> 00:20:40,282
We've only been filming for a bit.

309
00:20:41,082 --> 00:20:45,362
Mr. Zhang, thank you
for working with Zhen Xin.

310
00:20:45,362 --> 00:20:47,762
Tell you what,
I'll treat everyone to dinner tonight.

311
00:20:47,762 --> 00:20:48,922
How about hot pot?

312
00:20:48,922 --> 00:20:50,642
Don't go organizing things randomly.

313
00:20:50,642 --> 00:20:52,162
The crew is on a tight schedule.

314
00:20:52,162 --> 00:20:53,922
We don't have the time or energy to go.

315
00:20:53,922 --> 00:20:55,202
I'll go.

316
00:20:55,202 --> 00:20:57,522
Great, I'll arrange it.

317
00:21:15,042 --> 00:21:17,202
Where are you from, Mr. Zhang?

318
00:21:17,202 --> 00:21:19,722
I'm from Sichuan. I love spicy food.

319
00:21:19,722 --> 00:21:20,882
That's a shame.

320
00:21:20,882 --> 00:21:24,202
Mr. Zhen and I usually
don't really like spicy food.

321
00:21:24,202 --> 00:21:25,722
He has a weak stomach.

322
00:21:25,722 --> 00:21:29,562
How long have you two been together?

323
00:21:29,562 --> 00:21:32,722
We've... been together for almost a year?

324
00:21:32,722 --> 00:21:34,082
Not that long.

325
00:21:34,082 --> 00:21:36,162
We both have our own work.

326
00:21:36,162 --> 00:21:38,322
We don't even see each other once a month.

327
00:21:38,322 --> 00:21:42,402
But even so, we're still together.

328
00:21:42,402 --> 00:21:45,202
Isn't that true love, honey?

329
00:21:48,322 --> 00:21:49,762
Mr. Zhang.

330
00:21:49,762 --> 00:21:51,762
What about you?

331
00:21:51,762 --> 00:21:53,482
Me?

332
00:21:54,122 --> 00:21:55,922
I'm getting married soon.

333
00:21:58,002 --> 00:22:00,002
After I finish this project.

334
00:22:12,402 --> 00:22:14,122
Are you eating?

335
00:22:15,402 --> 00:22:16,842
Yeah. I'm free.

336
00:22:16,842 --> 00:22:18,342
Go ahead.

337
00:22:25,282 --> 00:22:29,642
Yesterday, why were you holding his hand?

338
00:22:31,282 --> 00:22:34,042
If I hadn't come,

339
00:22:34,042 --> 00:22:35,762
what would you have done?

340
00:22:41,882 --> 00:22:43,482
Look at this hot pot.

341
00:22:43,482 --> 00:22:45,682
The two pots are different.

342
00:22:45,682 --> 00:22:48,282
I don't care about your pot,

343
00:22:48,915 --> 00:22:51,682
but don't touch mine.

344
00:22:51,682 --> 00:22:56,682
Besides, that pot of yours is nothing much.

345
00:23:02,682 --> 00:23:03,842
Why aren't you eating?

346
00:23:03,842 --> 00:23:06,442
I was waiting for you to come back.

347
00:23:06,442 --> 00:23:08,922
This is cooked. Try it.

348
00:23:21,402 --> 00:23:23,402
Honey.

349
00:23:23,402 --> 00:23:26,842
Eating so much spicy food
is bad for your stomach.

350
00:23:28,042 --> 00:23:30,682
It's my stomach. I'll do as I please.

351
00:23:47,082 --> 00:23:48,802
Enjoy your meal.

352
00:23:50,322 --> 00:23:52,042
I have something to take care of.

353
00:23:56,605 --> 00:24:03,050
[Today is a good day]

354
00:24:17,802 --> 00:24:19,562
Why the hell are you calling?

355
00:24:19,562 --> 00:24:21,882
Come out if you have the guts!

356
00:24:21,882 --> 00:24:23,882
<i>It's me.</i>

357
00:24:28,802 --> 00:24:30,282
I'm sorry.

358
00:24:30,282 --> 00:24:31,480
I'm sorry.

359
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,980
Dan Yi.

360
00:24:34,282 --> 00:24:37,001
- I...
<i>- Are you okay?</i>

361
00:24:42,682 --> 00:24:44,482
I'm fine.

362
00:24:45,522 --> 00:24:49,242
<i>Are you... alone?</i>

363
00:24:51,202 --> 00:24:53,042
I was just with...

364
00:24:57,642 --> 00:24:59,562
a friend.

365
00:24:59,562 --> 00:25:01,802
I was with a friend.

366
00:25:04,842 --> 00:25:06,402
And...

367
00:25:11,402 --> 00:25:13,122
his girlfriend.

368
00:25:15,762 --> 00:25:17,642
<i>Are you coming back?</i>

369
00:25:19,682 --> 00:25:23,922
<i>When this is all over, will you come back?</i>

370
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:30,960
I...

371
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,720
Dan Yi.

372
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:40,040
I don't know.

373
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,760
<i>I can wait.</i>

374
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:45,040
<i>I mean, if you want to come back,</i>

375
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:46,960
<i>I'll be waiting for you at home.</i>

376
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:08,560
I'm sorry.

377
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,280
Please give me a little more time.

378
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:20,400
I need to find that answer.

379
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:32,000
I followed you out.

380
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:35,480
Zhang Zhun.

381
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:25,640
472 steps.

382
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,360
From the moment you left the restaurant,

383
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:35,200
you took exactly 472 steps.

384
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:41,360
You were on the phone,

385
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:43,840
and I was following behind you.

386
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:52,560
Like a stray dog.

387
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:25,320
Why are you...

388
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,960
crying?

389
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:48,360
I'll break up with her.

390
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:59,840
So will I.

391
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:34,840
Do you know what Chen Zheng Sen said about us?

392
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:44,400
He said...

393
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:48,240
we're finished.

394
00:30:15,931 --> 00:30:17,952
[Xie Dan Yi]

395
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:41,960
Don't chase after them.

396
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:50,400
What's the point even if you catch up?

397
00:30:58,806 --> 00:31:00,953
There's a bar nearby.

398
00:31:00,953 --> 00:31:02,753
Let's have a drink.

399
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:25,480
I don't know you.

400
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:27,300
You do now.

401
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,240
Don't worry.

402
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,640
There are cameras here.

403
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,880
It's very safe.

404
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:37,360
I'm Feng Yun Ting, Zhen Xin's girlfriend.

405
00:31:42,840 --> 00:31:45,080
I never drink.

406
00:31:52,324 --> 00:31:54,845
Get us a non-alcoholic drink, please.

407
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:02,160
Then why did you stop me just now?

408
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:04,880
Did you really want to chase them

409
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:07,240
just to be further humiliated?

410
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:11,240
Be better to yourself.

411
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:15,280
In this world, there are many things

412
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:17,040
you can't live without.

413
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:20,280
But a man is not one of them.

414
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:22,120
If you keep compromising,

415
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:25,200
you'll be the only one who suffers.

416
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:30,120
- Enjoy your drink.
- Thank you.

417
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:31,920
This one is non-alcoholic.

418
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,560
Take your time.

419
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:38,280
Are you really willing to give up?

420
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:41,240
Silly girl.

421
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,960
It's just like this drink.

422
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:45,600
I've already paid for it.

423
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:49,360
I can choose to frown and finish it,

424
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:52,122
or I can throw it in someone's face.

425
00:32:52,122 --> 00:32:54,442
As for what I'll do,

426
00:32:54,442 --> 00:32:57,522
it all depends on what makes me happy.

427
00:32:57,522 --> 00:33:00,842
Or... what makes my life better.

428
00:33:06,602 --> 00:33:07,922
Silly girl.

429
00:33:07,922 --> 00:33:10,722
Losing in love isn't shameful.

430
00:33:10,722 --> 00:33:14,722
But if you lose yourself,
that's when it gets ugly.

431
00:33:16,922 --> 00:33:18,722
Take your time with the drink.

432
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:23,780
I'm off.

433
00:33:57,842 --> 00:33:59,922
I'll take care of everything.

434
00:34:03,402 --> 00:34:05,202
Oh, for goodness sake.

435
00:34:05,202 --> 00:34:06,722
Reporters are camping out at the door.

436
00:34:06,722 --> 00:34:08,682
And you two are still being so flashy.

437
00:34:09,482 --> 00:34:10,527
Everyone's watching you.

438
00:34:10,527 --> 00:34:12,760
How can you still act like this?

439
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,520
You two, stay out of sight.

440
00:34:17,160 --> 00:34:19,360
Everyone, this is the crew's hotel.

441
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,840
- Please don't...
- Mr. Zhen!

442
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,560
You've been dating
Ms. Feng Yun Ting for half a year.

443
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:25,200
Why choose to go public now?

444
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:10,360
<i>If... you always dream about someone,</i>

445
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:12,600
<i>and the dreams are always intimate...</i>

446
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,560
<i>What does that mean?</i>

447
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:19,280
<i>Essentially, the subconscious is expressing
unfulfilled intimacy and sexual desire.</i>

448
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:23,200
<i>Also, this person symbolizes
a quality you desire.</i>

449
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:37,080
<i>Then...</i>

450
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:40,160
<i>does it mean I like them?</i>

451
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:46,160
<i>If the intimacy in the dream
makes you happy when you wake up,</i>

452
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:47,480
<i>and you want to be close to them,</i>

453
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:50,160
<i>and you follow their every move in real life,</i>

454
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:52,520
<i>then it's likely
your subconscious revealing itself.</i>

455
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:54,480
<i>It means you like them.</i>

456
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:16,040
Why aren't you sitting in the second row?

457
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:20,040
Do you know why Laozi wrote the Tao Te Ching?

458
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:23,960
Because he felt like it.

